    "Key Issues/Notes ⚫  Could be influenced by the support the project would generate for education. \n⚫ Wants a new wastewater plant and a new school for the city \n⚫ Does not want to raise taxes. \n⚫ Could be more influenced if water is recycled \n⚫ Supportive of new forms of revenue for the city.  ⚫ Unions can influence him. \n⚫ Water has been a major concern. ⚫ Former school board member and will value educational funding. \n⚫ May follow Will McIntosh’s position. ⚫ Active Democrat and can be influenced by local Democrats.  \n⚫ Environmentalist and also would be attracted by funding for education. \n⚫ Former school board member, like Holmes. ⚫ Understands business issues \n⚫ Does not want to raise taxes. ⚫ Workforce housing is a priority.\n⚫ Her district   ⚫ Would be influenced by employment opportunities and funding for education. \n⚫ Member of the Teamsters Union.": "",
